OL,6,FCharanpreet Khaira speaks to families
OL,7,Faffected by failings in maternity care
OL,8,Fin Bradford
OL,10,FA couple who were wrongly told their
OL,11,Funborn baby had died the day before
OL,12,Fshe was delivered fit and well say
OL,13,Fthey went through "hell and back".
OL,15,FJamal Mahboob and his wife Fozia Nazir
OL,16,Fwere told by doctors at Bradford Royal
OL,17,FInfirmary (BRI) that there was no
OL,18,Fheartbeat when they went for a routine
OL,19,Fscan 37 weeks into the pregnancy.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/14
