OL,3,CCouple wrongly told unborn baby had
OL,4,Cdied went through 'hell'
OL,6,FBut after being sent home they
OL,7,Freturned for a second scan hours later
OL,8,Fand were informed that their daughter
OL,9,Fwas alive.
OL,11,FShe was delivered the following day, 1
OL,12,FJanuary last year.
OL,14,FThe hospital trust later apologised
OL,15,Ffor the "emotional distress" caused by
OL,16,Fthe "misdiagnosis".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/14
