OL,3,CCouple wrongly told unborn baby had
OL,4,Cdied went through 'hell'
OL,6,FMr Mahboob said: "Me and my wife have
OL,7,Fbeen through hell and back. It was
OL,8,Fabsolutely devastating what we were
OL,9,Fgoing through, I would not wish that
OL,10,Fon anybody."
OL,12,FThe couple, who also have a four-year-
OL,13,Fold son, had faced a challenging
OL,14,Fpregnancy due to Mrs Nazir's diabetes
OL,15,Fand the fact that she had experienced
OL,16,Fsome difficulties before their son was
OL,17,Fborn.
OL,19,FBut there was no suggestion anything
OL,20,Fwas wrong before Mrs Nazir attended
OL,21,FBRI on 31 December 2023.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/14
