OL,6,FBusinessman Mr Mahboob said: "When she
OL,7,Fgot there and they did the scan they
OL,8,Fcouldn't find the baby's heart rate. I
OL,9,Fwent into the hospital, the consultant
OL,10,Fsat me down and he's giving me his
OL,11,Fcondolences - (he said) 'sorry for
OL,12,Fyour loss'."
OL,14,FThey were initially told to return
OL,15,Fhome until the following day, when a
OL,16,Fplan would be discussed for the baby
OL,17,Fto be stillborn.
