OL,6,FMr Mahboob said his wife continued to
OL,7,Ffeel movement, but medics claimed she
OL,8,Fwas merely struggling to accept the
OL,9,Floss of her child.
OL,11,FHe pushed for action to be taken that
OL,12,Fday and took his wife home for a
OL,13,Fnumber of hours, during which time
OL,14,Fthey began making funeral
OL,15,Farrangements, before returning that
OL,16,Fevening.
OL,18,F"We came home, obviously devastated as
OL,19,Fa family," he said. "We're heartbroken
OL,20,F- you can't imagine it.
