OL,6,FIn a letter seen by ITV Calendar,
OL,7,FBradford Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,8,Foffered "sincere apologies for your
OL,9,Fexperience and emotional distress when
OL,10,Fyou attended the maternity service on
OL,11,F31 December 2023 and the misdiagnosis
OL,12,Fthat your baby had died in the womb
OL,13,Fwas made".
OL,15,FThe couple's case is among a number
OL,16,Ftaken up by the Labour MP for Bradford
OL,17,FWest Naz Shah, who has written to
OL,18,Fhealth secretary Wes Streeting over
OL,19,Fconcerns about the trust's leadership.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/14
