OL,6,FIt comes after claims whistleblowers
OL,7,Fwho had tried to raise problems with
OL,8,Fcare had been ignored.
OL,10,FLauren Caulfield's daughter, Grace,
OL,11,Fdied in 2022 after medics failed to
OL,12,Fnotice problems with her pregnancy.
OL,14,F"Nobody had picked up on the fact that
OL,15,Fher growth had completely tailed off,"
OL,16,Fshe said.
OL,18,F"My concerns about reduced movements
OL,19,Fwere ignored when they shouldn't have
OL,20,Fbeen.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/14
