OL,3,CCouple wrongly told unborn baby had
OL,4,Cdied went through 'hell'
OL,6,F"I was a first time mum, I was 24, I
OL,7,Fwas quite young and anxious,
OL,8,Funderstandably anxious, but I was
OL,9,Flooked at as an over-worried, silly
OL,10,Fgirl at the time. when in hindsight if
OL,11,Feven one person had listened in those
OL,12,Fappointments to my concerns, Grace
OL,13,Fwould be here today and she would be
OL,14,Fnearly three years old."
OL,16,FA report later found the rate of
OL,17,Fneonatal deaths at Bradford's hospital
OL,18,Fwas three times above the national
OL,19,Ftarget amount.
