OL,6,FThe hospital trust said it had
OL,7,Fimplemented changes since Grace's
OL,8,Fdeath and was "committed to learning
OL,9,Ffrom this incident to improve outcomes
OL,10,Ffor all mums and their babies".
OL,12,F'This is about accountability'
OL,14,FLast year BRI's neonatal unit was
OL,15,Frated as outstanding by the Care
OL,16,FQuality Commission, but inspectors
OL,17,Fsaid its maternity services still
OL,18,Frequired improvement.
