OL,6,FIt followed an unannounced inspection
OL,7,Fafter whistleblowers and patients
OL,8,Fraised concerns about safe care and
OL,9,Ftreatment in some units.
OL,11,FHowever, Ms Shah said she remained
OL,12,F"very worried for my constituents who
OL,13,Fhave no choice but to go to that
OL,14,Fhospital".
OL,16,FShe said: "The confidence in the
OL,17,Fcommunity has to be at a strength to
OL,18,Fbe able to access service to have the
OL,19,Fconfidence in the service and that
OL,20,Fdoesn't exist at this moment.
