OL,6,F"Ultimately this is about
OL,7,Faccountability, this is about
OL,8,Fgovernance, this is about anybody who
OL,9,Fdares to ask the question or sew the
OL,10,Fthreads together (being) retaliated
OL,11,Fagainst or is driven out, suspended -
OL,12,For there is an attempt to remove them.
OL,13,FThat's not okay."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Bradford Teaching
OL,16,FHospitals NHS Trust said it could not
OL,17,Fcomment on Ms Shah's claims as
OL,18,F"matters are ongoing".
